Exercise 012 - Print what you get before exit - Solutions

1) Supposing your user is "mmul" and your machine is "machine":

> ssh mmul@machine

2) This script sets up a trap for SIGINT and SIGTERM.
   These are the equivalent of the CTRL+C key combination.
   
   In order to test the trap, yu have to send this signal to the script.
   
   Once caught the signal, it exits.
